致谢
值此论文编写工作即将完成之际，本人谨向所有给予我指导、关心、支持和帮助的 老师、领导、同学和亲人表示最诚挚的谢意！
首先，我要衷心感谢我的导师李平研究员，本文从选题到撰写完成都是在李老师的 悉心指导下完成的。李老师严谨的治学态度、求实创新的科研作风、渊博的学识、丰富 的实践经验、平易近人的为人风范，都使我受益匪浅。感谢李老师三年来在学习和生活 上给予我的关心和帮助。
感谢马小宁博士、邹丹、刘彦军、杨连报、武威、孙思齐以及项目组其他同志在我 论文撰写过程中给予的帮助。
感谢研修学院的老师以及 15 级硕士班的同学们，在研究生学习期间给我学习、生 活上的关心和帮助；感谢关心我的家人和朋友们，他们在精神和物质上都给予我极大的 帮助和支持，使我得以顺利完成学业和论文。
感谢给予我帮助的大数据中心领导和同事们，大数据中心给我提供了良好的学习和 科研环境，使我在这里获益良多。
最后向百忙之中抽出时间来评阅论文的专家、教授致以最衷心的感谢！

中国铁道科学研究院硕士学位论文
摘要
随着大数据时代的来临，以及大数据技术应用的愈加广泛，数据已经变成企业的重 要资产之一。通过对数据的分析挖掘及应用，可以有效提升企业的管理水平及经济效益。 在铁路运输领域，通过近四十年的铁路信息化建设，中国铁路总公司已经建成了大量的 业务信息系统，并积累了海量的 PB 级规模数据，为大数据在铁路行业的应用奠定了坚 实的数据基础。但由于铁路信息系统建设初期对主数据管理的概念薄弱，各业务系统独 立建设、分散维护，造成铁路基础数据标准不统一、编码不统一、含义不一致，给数据 共享和数据关联分析带来极大困难。特别是进入大数据分析时代，对数据质量提出了更 高要求。因此，通过建设铁路主数据管理平台实现对铁路主数据的规范及高效管理，对 提升铁路数据质量、促进大数据技术在铁路行业的广泛应用具有重要意义。本文主要的 研究内容如下：
（1）提出了铁路主数据的定义、特点及内涵，在分析铁路主数据管理需求的基础 上，设计了铁路主数据管理平台的总体架构，分别从主数据集成、存储、治理、发布等 方面对平台的功能架构进行了设计，并对基于信息分类法建立的铁路主数据管理数据架 构进行阐述。
（2）针对从多源异构异域复杂业务系统中识别铁路主数据的需求，本文提出了基 于模糊层次分析法的铁路主数据识别模型，并应用知识图谱技术对铁路主数据进行了建 模。
（3）设计了铁路主数据管理的全生命周期模型，并对铁路主数据维护流程进行阐 述，分别从主数据的集成、存储及发布等方面进行创新，提出了基于模板的数据清洗及 导入、基于 WebService 的数据接入、铁路主数据属性动态映射、大数据量文件共享、基 于时间戳的数据版本管理及追溯等关键技术。
（4）以大数据应用为目的，研究提出了基于主数据标准进行数据采集和数据治理 的方法。阐述了基于铁路数据服务平台的数据采集实现，并在大数据治理中应用铁路主 数据标准对业务数据进行清洗，有效提升了铁路数据服务平台的数据质量。
（5）研发实现了铁路主数据管理平台的核心功能，对总体架构、关键技术等进行了 验证，并介绍了铁路主数据管理平台的应用效果。 关键词：铁路信息化；主数据管理；大数据应用
I

中国铁道科学研究院硕士学位论文
Abstract
With the advent of the big data era and the wider application of big data technology, the data has become one of the company's important assets. Through the analysis and application of the data, the management level and economic benefit can be improved effectively. In the field of railway transportation, through nearly 40 years of railway informatization construction, the China Railway Company has built a large number of business information systems and accumulated a large amount of data, laying a solid data foundation for the application of big data in the railway industry. However, due to the weak concept of master data management in the early stage of railway information system construction, each business system was independently constructed and decentralized maintained, resulting in inconsistent railway data standards, coding, and meanings. It have caused great difficulties in data sharing and data correlation. Especially in the era of big data analysis, higher requirements have been put on data quality. Therefore, achieving the construction of unified and efficient railway master data management platform is of great significance to improving the quality of railway data and promoting the widespread application of big data technology in the railway industry. The main research content of this paper is as follows:
(1) The definition, characteristics and connotation of railway master data were proposed. The relationship between big data application and master data management was analyzed. Based on analysis of railway master data management requirements, the overall architecture of the railway master data management platform was designed and proposed. The functional architecture of the platform was designed from the aspects of master data integration, master data storage, and master data release. Through combing the master data of railway with information classification, this thesis establishes the data structure of railway master data management.
(2) For the demand of identifying railway master data from complex business system, this thesis puts forward a railway master data recognition model based on fuzzy analytic hierarchy process. And it uses knowledge graph technology to establish a model of railway master data.
(3) The whole lifecycle model of railway master data management was designed, and innovations were made from the aspects of master data integration, master data storage, and master data release. Such as data cleaning and importing based on templates, data accessing
III

中国铁道科学研究院硕士学位论文
based on WebService, dynamic properties of railway master data mapping, large amount of file sharing, date-based data version management and traceability and other key technologies were proposed.
(4) For the purpose of big data applications, a method for data integration and data governance based on master data standards was proposed. The master data integration based on the Railway Data Service Platform is described, and the railway master data standard is used to clean the business data in the big data governance, which improves the data quality of the Railway Data Service Platform.
(5) Research and development to achieve the core functions of master data management platform of the railway, and verify the overall architecture and key technologies. And systematically evaluated the application effect of the railway master data management platform. Key Words: Railway Informatization; Master Data Management; Big Data Applications
IV

